### Extension 4: LazyGolf API / Data Products

**Concept:** Monetize golf data collected through the platform.

#### Data Products

| Product | Customer | Price |
|---------|----------|-------|
| Handicap Tracking API | Other golf apps | $0.01/request |
| League Stats Embed | Golf blogs/media | $19/mo |
| Aggregate Trends Report | Golf industry | $500/report |
