- Higher margin, more complexity

#### Product Categories

| Category | Example Products |
|----------|------------------|
| Phones | Simple smartphones, flip phones |
| Tablets | Large-screen tablets with cases |
| Video Calling | Portal, Echo Show alternatives |
| Safety | Medical alert devices |
| Accessories | Large-button remotes, magnifiers |

#### Viability Assessment

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | Medium |
| Effort | Low (affiliate) to High (white-label) |
| Revenue | $5K-50K/yr depending on model |
| Moat | Trust + curation |

