## ndev Consulting Extensions

### Extension 1: Specialized Consulting Practices

**Concept:** Spin off specialized practices from general ndev consulting.

#### Practice Areas

| Practice | Focus | Target Client |
|----------|-------|---------------|
| **ndev AI** | LLM/RAG integration | Enterprises exploring AI |
| **ndev Golf Tech** | Golf industry software | Courses, equipment cos |
| **ndev Local-First** | Offline-capable apps | Privacy-focused companies |

#### Why Spin Off

- Different branding for different markets
- Specialized positioning commands premium rates
- Can be separate entities or brands under ndev
- Easier to sell/partner individual practices

---

### Extension 2: ndev Agency (Subcontractor Network)

**Concept:** Formalize subcontractor relationships into an agency model.

#### Structure

| Role | Count | Focus |
|------|-------|-------|
| Travis | 1 | Architecture, sales, key client relationships |
| Senior Devs | 1-2 | Complex implementation |
| Mid Devs | 2-3 | Standard development |
| Specialists | As needed | Design, DevOps, etc. |

#### Revenue Model

| Model | Your Cut | Subcontractor |
|-------|----------|---------------|
| Client pays $150/hr | $50/hr (33%) | $100/hr |
| Fixed price projects | 25-40% margin | Rest |

#### Viability Assessment

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | High |
| Effort | Medium (management overhead) |
| Revenue | $200K-500K/yr at scale |
| Moat | Relationships + reliability |

**Trade-off:** More revenue, but more management and less personal work.

