## Prioritized Extension Roadmap

### Now (Can Start This Month)

1. **LazyGolf Content** - Start YouTube/newsletter before platform launches
2. **ndev Retainer Packages** - Formalize existing work

### After LazyGolf Platform MVP (3-6 months)

3. **LazyGolf Pro (B2B)** - Add business tier to platform
4. **Golf Betting Calculator** - Quick standalone app

### After Rent-a-Nerd Validation (6-12 months)

5. **Rent-a-Nerd Training Platform** - Courses for common issues
6. **Senior Tech Product Curation** - Affiliate store

### Scale Phase (12+ months)

7. **LazyGolf Marketplace** - Once you have audience
8. **Rent-a-Nerd License Model** - Once proven locally
9. **ndev Agency** - When turning down work consistently

